column2: SELECT TOP #   m.specz_id,   m.specz_ra,      m.specz_dec,   (m.specz_redshift - f.z)/m.specz_redshift AS z_distance,   n.objid,    n.distance,   f.z,    f.zErr,    f.specobjid,   f.petroMag_g - f.petroMag_i AS gminusi,   sm.logMass,    sm.logMass_err,   sm.ssfr + sm.logMass - #. AS logSFR,   sm.age,   p.petroR9#_i,   p.petroR5#_i,   p.petroR9#_i / p.petroR5#_i AS concentration  FROM MyDB.sdssmatches_s1#a AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.specz_ra, m.specz_dec, #) AS n    JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS f ON n.objid=f.objid    JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as sm on f.SpecObjID = sm.SpecObjID   JOIN PhotoObj as p ON f.objid = p.objID
